
Request-StackAPI.ps1 version 1.0
==================================================================================
This is a sample program to Access CloudStack API.

Please refer to the following for detail of CloudStack API.

 API Reference Guide
<http://docs.cloud.com/CloudStack_Documentation/API_Reference%3A_CloudStack>

 Developer's Guide: CloudStack
<http://cloud.mindtouch.us/CloudStack_Documentation/Developer's_Guide%3A_CloudStack>


DEPENDENCIES

This script is tested at Windows Server 2008 R2 SP1 and
Powershell v2.0. .NET Framework 2.0 or newer version is
Required.


